        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 65421e60-fb36-4e2a-bdb5-738a4197bad7).Image",
        "Description": "Hello, 47.\r\rYour target today is Calimero Endrizzi, currently working as a bodyguard for the politician Marco Abbiati. In 1990 he moved to Kosovo, in 1992 he joined the UCK, in 1994 he participated in the murder of 16 Serbian civilians. After that, Interpol issued a warrant for him, then he changed his name Afak Pojani to Calimero Endrizzi. He appeared after 30 years on the run, he began collaborating with the Albanian mafia, becoming the leader of the mafia on the Amalfi Coast.\r\rGood Luck, 47.",
